#5 Cookie Invalidation after changing password

Summary: When user changes password the old session is not expiring, which causes a bug.
Steps to reproduce: Login to your account in 2 browsers, change passsword one and go to the second browser and reload the page, and you can see the session is still active in that browser.
Impact: Due to this bug, there is no way for the victim to revoke access of attacker if account has been already compromised.
